{"tid":485612,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【求救】大頭蝦唔撚見咗個銀包","createTime":"2017-12-01T05:59:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-01T06:37:45.000Z","uid":152069,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d2306d2b805d215d705f2d59feb943110907a1df","tid":485612,"uid":152069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T05:59:48.000Z","msg":"懇求各位巴絲幫下手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日小妹係九龍灣巴士站落車後就唔見咗個銀包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小妹嘅路線係淘大往九龍灣站嘅天橋一直行經過德福商場直去大業街 之後先發現唔見咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個銀包係皮質深藍色，唔大，入面有匯豐卡同八達通同埋學生證有個用$100褶成嘅心心仲有好少現金<br />\n如果有好心人執到，可唔可以直接tg我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/kty331\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fkty331&d=EsbRmfGEyIqgtGSc2fR%2Bh%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=f94f951a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/kty331</a><br />\npush<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n感激不盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多謝你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連登有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00f3099b6925dae5b73ed2f054e3a751a57a235f"